    "summary": "After a career in the Transport, Energy and Telecommunications industry I started in 2004 my own company in providing outstanding IT interim- and project management  services to multinational companies.  15 years later we have a solid base in the Benelux serving customers in the region as well globally. Our focus is on IT Delivery- , Workplace Transformation Management and IT (Infrastructure) Services migrations and consolidations for regional and global IT organizations.\n\nGuaranteed success based on:\n1)  active participation between Business, IT and users\n2)  use of proven and effective migration methodology and tools.\n\nOverview of successes:\n* In time & budget delivery of large scale and complex regional and global Desktop Migrations \n  (4.000- 205.000 seats across 220 countries)\n* In time upgrade, in- and outsourcing of large local, regional and global IT infrastructure environments.\n* Consolidation and transition of IT services from countries into regional data centers and\n   global data centers.\n* Harmonization of ITIL processes of local IT country organizations in Europe. \n* Consolidation of global and regional Datacenters.\n* Rightsizing and outsourcing of WAN for top 100 companies.\n* Post merger consolidation of IT Service Management processes.\n\nSpecialization: IT Delivery-, Workplace Transformation Management and IT (Infrastructure) Services Migration  Programs.\n\nPlease visit the website for more information on IDM and our IT solutions: http://www.itdeliverymanagement.com",
