                    "description": "IT Delivery Management (IDM) brings transparency into the complex world of IT delivery and IT management. Instant transparency \u2013 by offering a direct, clear and unobstructed view on the effectiveness and efficiency of IT resources. \n\nWe provide seemingly simple solutions to address often-asked questions in IT management. \n\nWe have a solution for you if you have questions such as: \u2018how are services and components performing\u2019, \u2018how can we keep an eye on country IT, on premise data centers, outsourcers and/or cloud providers\u2019? And: \u2018why is it that we can't seem to get the right information or usage out our IT resources?\u2019, \u2018how can we adopt a more predictive and pre-emptive approach in IT management?\u2019, \u2018how can we get the most of the money we spend in IT management? And: \u2018How can we be more agile for the business without waiting months following paper trails or escalations?\u2019\n\nOur solutions \u2013 eView, eTransition, eDecision and eDeploy \u2013 provide the transparency and control that every professional in IT delivery craves for \u2013 be it management summary level or the last technical detail.",
